title: “Drunk on Coup-laid.”
description: The U.S. launches the largest vaccination effort in history as the first doses of Pfizer’s vaccine are delivered, the Electoral College meets to formalize Joe Biden’s victory, and the Republican Party chooses Donald Trump over democracy.
author: hey@crooked.com (Crooked Media)
